table = df.pivot_table(index='churn', values=df.columns, aggfunc='mean').T.reset_index().rename_axis(None, axis=1)
table.columns = ['features', 'stay_mean', 'leave_mean']
table['coef'] = table['leave_mean'] / table['stay_mean']
table = table.sort_values(by='coef', ascending=False).reset_index(drop=True)

In [22]:
def make_prediction(m, X_train, y_train, X_test, y_test):
    model = m
    model.fit(X_train, y_train)
    y_pred = model.predict(X_test)
    print(
        'Accuracy:{:.2f} Precision:{:.2f} Recall:{:.2f} '.format(
            accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred),
            precision_score(y_test, y_pred),
            recall_score(y_test, y_pred)
        )
    )
